'''Guardians''' were [[Battle droid/Legends|battle droids]] produced by [[Tendrando Arms]]. An improved version of the [[Defender Droid]], it had thick weapons-equipped arms, gray [[Laminanium/Legends|laminanium]] armor, higher than military standard [[mag-shielding]], and a downward-pointing [[Vocabulator/Legends|vocabulator]]. Without proper authorization, the droid could not be shut down. One was used to keep [[Cal Omas]] under house arrest.

